1. Add this alias in laptops windows etc/hosts
192.168.24.48 gitlab

2. Connect NetExtender VPN

3.  Reset password :   http://gitlab/users/password/new?user_email=hector.barriga%40tangotelecom.com

4. Login http://gitlab/users/sign_in
Notes:
- gitlab account is hbarriga. You can also login with tango email account

hbarriga (or hector.barriga@tangotelecom.com)
Password = Personal one


5. Configure ssh connecton to gitlab server
Notes:
- You wont be able to ssh to gitlab machine (no bash console account/password). So you need to add it via gitlab GUI << Step 5.1
- You will receive an email after added << Step 5.1
- If not using sshuttle (It is not perfect), you will still need to configure ssh connection to be able to use git command to pull respositories from gitlab server (192.168.24.48). Note: No need to run ssh command since it is not needed (The git uses http) and besides we dont have that server's root or tango's password   << Step  5.3

5.1 Add /root/.ssh/rsa_id.pub in gitlab via GUI only
Notes: 
- You must have created  /root/.ssh/rsa_id.pub on my DEVOPS-HECTOR-VM1. Use passwordless steps from "usual comands.txt" guide
- Copy key on gitlab GUI. Set any "title"

http://gitlab/profile/keys

5.2 Add gitlab alias in /etc/hosts <<<<<<<< My DEVOPS-HECTOR-VM1 (runs on my laptop)
/etc/hosts
192.168.24.48 gitlab


5.3 Add this Host in /root/.ssh/config          <<<<<<<<< Skip this step if using sshuttle. For Mobily PCF, you have to use this
Host gitlab
        Hostname gitlab
        User root
        IdentityFile /root/.ssh/id_rsa
        ProxyCommand ssh hector@86.43.69.175 -p 15202 -W %h:%p
		
		
6. Configure your account "hbarriga" in your laptop "DEVOPS-HECTOR-VM1" git. This is done once in order for "DEVOPS-HECTOR-VM1" to download (pull) repositories/projects from Tango gitlab directly from tango gitlab without having to put user name all the time 
6.1 Add user and email
git config --global user.name "hbarriga"
git config --global user.email hector.barriga@tangotelecom.com

6.2 Checks
6.2.1 Check /root/.gitconfig is created
[root@DEVOPS-HECTOR-VM1 15:55:15 ~]# cat /root/.gitconfig
[user]
        name = hbarriga
        email = hector.barriga@tangotelecom.com

6.2.2 Lists
[root@DEVOPS-HECTOR-VM1 15:55:43 source]# git config --global --list
user.name=hbarriga
user.email=hector.barriga@tangotelecom.com




